## Recent auto-decisions（最近自动决策）

展示最近 10 个由 PreToolUse hook auto-decided 的 questions（log 中 source=
`auto-decided`）。让用户 spot-check enforcement，并把任何 misfire 的项切换为
`always-ask`。

```bash
eval "$(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-slug 2>/dev/null)"
eval "$(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-paths)"
_LOG="$GSTACK_STATE_ROOT/projects/$SLUG/question-log.jsonl"
[ ! -f "$_LOG" ] && echo 'NO_LOG' || bun -e "
  const lines = require('fs').readFileSync('$_LOG','utf-8').trim().split('\n').filter(Boolean);
  const auto = [];
  for (const l of lines) {
    try { const e = JSON.parse(l); if (e.source === 'auto-decided') auto.push(e); } catch {}
  }
  const recent = auto.slice(-10).reverse();
  if (!recent.length) { console.log('(no auto-decisions yet)'); process.exit(0); }
  for (const r of recent) {
    console.log(r.ts + '  ' + r.question_id + ' → ' + r.user_choice);
    console.log('     ' + (r.question_summary || ''));
  }
"
```

如果有看起来不对的项，提供："Want to flip `<question_id>` to `always-ask`?"
得到 Y 后运行 `gstack-question-preference --write '{"question_id":"<id>","preference":
"always-ask","source":"plan-tune"}'`。

---

## Audit unmarked questions（审计未标记问题）

按频率展示 top N hash-only question_ids。这些是 cathedral hook 捕获到、但无法 enforce 的
AUQ fires（skill template 中没有 `<gstack-qid:foo>` marker，即 D18 progressive markers）。
展示它们会推动 marker adoption：高流量 unmarked questions 是下一批 retrofit candidates。

```bash
eval "$(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-slug 2>/dev/null)"
eval "$(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-paths)"
_LOG="$GSTACK_STATE_ROOT/projects/$SLUG/question-log.jsonl"
[ ! -f "$_LOG" ] && echo 'NO_LOG' || bun -e "
  const lines = require('fs').readFileSync('$_LOG','utf-8').trim().split('\n').filter(Boolean);
  const counts = {};
  const summaries = {};
  for (const l of lines) {
    try {
      const e = JSON.parse(l);
      if (e.question_id && e.question_id.startsWith('hook-')) {
        counts[e.question_id] = (counts[e.question_id] || 0) + 1;
        summaries[e.question_id] = e.question_summary || '';
      }
    } catch {}
  }
  const rows = Object.entries(counts).sort((a,b) => b[1] - a[1]).slice(0, 10);
  if (!rows.length) { console.log('(no unmarked questions — coverage is 100%)'); process.exit(0); }
  for (const [id, n] of rows) {
    console.log(n + 'x  ' + id);
    console.log('     ' + summaries[id]);
  }
"
```

对每一行，建议 marker 应该放在哪里（根据 summary wording 查找 skill，例如
"Bundle this fix..." 可能位于 `ship/SKILL.md.tmpl`）。没有用户批准不要写 markers，
因为添加 markers 会改变哪些 AUQ fires 可以被 auto-decided，这属于 substrate expansion。

